{
 "fragments": [
  {
   "begin": "0.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "3.880", 
   "id": "s000001", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sehr geehrte Frau Pr\u00e4sidentin! "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "3.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "5.400", 
   "id": "s000002", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Liebe Kolleginnen und Kollegen! "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "5.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "6.920", 
   "id": "s000003", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir unterhalten uns hier \u00fcber die Frage: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "6.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "8.280", 
   "id": "s000004", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wie gef\u00e4hrlich ist es, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "8.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "11.360", 
   "id": "s000005", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wenn wir langfristig Stickoxide einatmen? "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "11.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "13.360", 
   "id": "s000006", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Um es ganz klar zu sagen: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "13.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "14.760", 
   "id": "s000007", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Es ist gef\u00e4hrlich. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "14.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "16.960", 
   "id": "s000008", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Es ist auch vollkommen unstrittig, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "16.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "20.480", 
   "id": "s000009", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass Stickoxide das Gewebe in den Lungen sch\u00e4digen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "20.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "26.160", 
   "id": "s000010", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass sie Herz-Kreislauf-Beschwerden verst\u00e4rken und dass sie Allergien hervorrufen."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "26.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "28.800", 
   "id": "s000011", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Um die Gesundheit von uns allen zu sch\u00fctzen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "28.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "33.880", 
   "id": "s000012", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "gibt es ebendiesen Jahresgrenzwert von 40\u00a0Mikrogramm pro Kubikmeter Luft. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "33.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "37.960", 
   "id": "s000013", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Er gilt f\u00fcr alle Menschen an allen Orten und zu jeder Zeit. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "37.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "41.160", 
   "id": "s000014", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Damit ist dieser Grenzwert darauf ausgelegt, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "41.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "45.360", 
   "id": "s000015", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass auch empfindliche Menschen keine Probleme bekommen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "45.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "49.800", 
   "id": "s000016", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Dieser Grenzwert ist nicht aus der Luft gegriffen."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "49.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "53.240", 
   "id": "s000017", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "\u2013\u00a0Dar\u00fcber k\u00f6nnen Sie ruhig lachen.\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "53.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "57.680", 
   "id": "s000018", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Epidemiologische Studien sind wissenschaftlich anerkannte Verfahren. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "57.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "58.680", 
   "id": "s000019", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ich finde es nicht gut, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "58.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "59.600", 
   "id": "s000020", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Frau Skudelny, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "59.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "67.440", 
   "id": "s000021", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass Sie diese mit komischen Vergleichen \u00fcber dicke B\u00e4uche von Ehem\u00e4nnern in Misskredit bringen."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "67.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "72.960", 
   "id": "s000022", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Experimentelle Versuche an Menschen und Tieren verbieten sich. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "72.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "76.480", 
   "id": "s000023", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Deshalb muss man auf diese Studien zur\u00fcckgreifen."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "76.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "83.440", 
   "id": "s000024", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Der Unterschied zwischen Grenzwerten im Allgemeinen und den Grenzwerten am Arbeitsplatz wurde gerade schon angedeutet. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "83.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "84.800", 
   "id": "s000025", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ich will hier keinen belehren, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "84.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "88.360", 
   "id": "s000026", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "aber vielleicht muss man es doch noch einmal sagen: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "88.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "92.120", 
   "id": "s000027", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Der entsprechende Grenzwert errechnet sich aus zwei Sicherheitsfaktoren, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "92.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "94.480", 
   "id": "s000028", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die miteinander multipliziert werden. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "94.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "99.760", 
   "id": "s000029", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ein Arbeitsleben dauert bei uns typischerweise 40\u00a0Jahre \u00e0 220\u00a0Arbeitstage. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "99.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "102.760", 
   "id": "s000030", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Diese Zahl mal acht Stunden ergibt etwa 70\u00a0000\u00a0Stunden. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "102.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "112.360", 
   "id": "s000031", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Bei einer Lebenserwartung von 80\u00a0Jahren atmet man aber in 700\u00a0000\u00a0Stunden insgesamt zehnmal so viel Luft ein und aus wie am Arbeitsplatz. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "112.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "118.760", 
   "id": "s000032", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Dazu kommt eine um den Faktor zwei bis f\u00fcnf erh\u00f6hte Empfindlichkeit von 10\u00a0Prozent der Bev\u00f6lkerung, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "118.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "120.440", 
   "id": "s000033", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die zwar \u00fcberwiegend gesund, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "120.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "121.200", 
   "id": "s000034", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "aber empfindlich sind. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "121.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "122.280", 
   "id": "s000035", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das sind zum Beispiel Kinder; "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "122.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "123.480", 
   "id": "s000036", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "sie wurden schon erw\u00e4hnt. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "123.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "125.600", 
   "id": "s000037", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Multipliziert man diese Faktoren, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "125.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "134.000", 
   "id": "s000038", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dann kommt man auf einen Wert von 20 bis 50\u00a0Mikrogramm pro Kubikmeter als einen vorsorgeorientierten Wert."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "134.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "135.560", 
   "id": "s000039", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Aber seien Sie doch ehrlich: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "135.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "136.720", 
   "id": "s000040", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Worum geht es hier wirklich? "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "136.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "138.280", 
   "id": "s000041", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Was ist hier die Frage? "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "138.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "140.760", 
   "id": "s000042", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Soll die Politik Vorsorge betreiben, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "140.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "142.560", 
   "id": "s000043", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und wie intensiv soll sie das machen? "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "142.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "144.640", 
   "id": "s000044", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir Gr\u00fcne finden, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "144.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "145.360", 
   "id": "s000045", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "es ist richtig, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "145.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "148.200", 
   "id": "s000046", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "das Vorsorgeprinzip streng anzuwenden,"
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "148.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "152.920", 
   "id": "s000047", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "damit Schwangere sich keine Sorgen um ihre Babys machen m\u00fcssen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "152.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "160.840", 
   "id": "s000048", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "damit auch alte Menschen die Luft in ihrer Stra\u00dfe atmen k\u00f6nnen und damit auch Menschen mit Asthma sich noch nach drau\u00dfen trauen k\u00f6nnen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "160.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "161.440", 
   "id": "s000049", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Und ja, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "161.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "163.880", 
   "id": "s000050", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "das Vorsorgeprinzip schlie\u00dft auch ein, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "163.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "167.440", 
   "id": "s000051", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass der Staat das freie Spiel des Marktes dort einengt, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "167.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "168.640", 
   "id": "s000052", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wo es n\u00f6tig ist, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "168.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "171.800", 
   "id": "s000053", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und das gilt jetzt insbesondere auch f\u00fcr die Autoindustrie. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "171.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "174.080", 
   "id": "s000054", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sie liegt n\u00e4mlich keinesfalls am Boden, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "174.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "175.840", 
   "id": "s000055", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "sondern macht Milliardengewinne, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "175.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "178.160", 
   "id": "s000056", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und zwar indem sie daran gespart hat, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "178.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "181.520", 
   "id": "s000057", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "eine ordentliche Abgasreinigung in ihre Autos einzubauen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "181.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "183.760", 
   "id": "s000058", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "obwohl sie es k\u00f6nnte. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "183.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "187.560", 
   "id": "s000059", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das ist n\u00e4mlich der wahre Skandal in dieser ganzen Diskussion, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "187.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "192.320", 
   "id": "s000060", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "liebe Kolleginnen und Kollegen."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "192.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "197.520", 
   "id": "s000061", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Aber zur\u00fcck zu den magischen 40\u00a0Mikrogramm Stickoxiden pro Kubikmeter Luft. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "197.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "199.880", 
   "id": "s000062", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Grenzwerte sind immer relativ, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "199.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "201.360", 
   "id": "s000063", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "aber man kann sie pr\u00fcfen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "201.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "202.400", 
   "id": "s000064", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das wird gemacht, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "202.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "204.000", 
   "id": "s000065", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und dann stellt man fest: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "204.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "207.320", 
   "id": "s000066", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Der heutige Grenzwert ist sogar eher zu lasch als zu streng. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "207.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "209.240", 
   "id": "s000067", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Nur weil wir ihn nicht einhalten, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "209.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "210.840", 
   "id": "s000068", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "ist er nicht falsch. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "210.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "213.000", 
   "id": "s000069", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das Problem l\u00f6st man nicht, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "213.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "218.160", 
   "id": "s000070", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "indem man Grenzwerte verschiebt oder die Messstation ein bisschen weiter weg aufstellt."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "218.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "227.760", 
   "id": "s000071", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "2015 haben sich die Experten der Weltgesundheitsorganisation alle Studien zur Langzeitwirkung von Stickoxiden noch einmal genau angeschaut. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "227.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "229.240", 
   "id": "s000072", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sie kamen zu dem Schluss, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "229.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "238.680", 
   "id": "s000073", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass mit gesundheitsrelevanten Wirkungen bei einer langfristigen durchschnittlichen Exposition von 20\u00a0Mikrogramm kalkuliert werden m\u00fcsse, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "238.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "240.320", 
   "id": "s000074", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und empfehlen sogar, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "240.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "244.040", 
   "id": "s000075", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "den Grenzwert bei der n\u00e4chsten Revision zu versch\u00e4rfen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "244.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "249.360", 
   "id": "s000076", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Dem schlie\u00dfen sich auch Experten aus dem Sachverst\u00e4ndigenrat f\u00fcr Umweltfragen an. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "249.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "250.960", 
   "id": "s000077", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sogar der VDI, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "250.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "253.080", 
   "id": "s000078", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "der nun wirklich nicht gr\u00fcnennah ist, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "253.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "254.200", 
   "id": "s000079", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "hat das best\u00e4tigt, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "254.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "256.840", 
   "id": "s000080", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und zwar 2004 und 2017."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "256.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "259.480", 
   "id": "s000081", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Genau vor diesem Hintergrund empfehle ich Ihnen: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "259.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "261.480", 
   "id": "s000082", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Weg mit dem Schaum vorm Mund, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "261.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "263.440", 
   "id": "s000083", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wenn es um Grenzwerte geht!"
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "263.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "266.480", 
   "id": "s000084", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Machen Sie sich bitte einmal Gedanken dar\u00fcber, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "266.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "267.600", 
   "id": "s000085", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "ob es nicht besser ist, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "267.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "272.040", 
   "id": "s000086", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "mit hohen Anforderungen die Wirtschaft gut f\u00fcr die Zukunft aufzustellen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "272.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "275.240", 
   "id": "s000087", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "ganz im Sinne von Lebensqualit\u00e4t und Gesundheit der Menschen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "275.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "278.040", 
   "id": "s000088", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und zwar der Gesundheit von allen Menschen!"
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "278.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "281.760", 
